Each release of the Demo Tool is equipped with binaries for Windows and Linux operating systems, and signed firmware images (ELFs) for MPD and iPerf3 applications. Though this document specifically describes the use of the GUI on a Windows platform, the procedure is similar for Linux OS as well. The content of the release is shown in Figure 1

Application INP_T2_Demo_Windows.exe is for Windows platform while INP_T2_Demo_Linux is for the Linux OS.
